default Research in Italy has found that a village where half the businesses are emloyee owned has a 
defaulthealthier community compared to a nearby village with no employee ownership. This encompassed more equality, larger social networks, children stayed at school longer, higher turnout at elections, less conspicuous consumption, more disposable income and les
defaults stress-related illnesses 
default(Erdall, David, 2011: 241)
